snippet.title: Man Hasn't Showered In 60 Years

localized.description:
He claims cleanliness brings him sickness.

By that logic, you'd probably smoke animal turds, too.

Amou Haji, an 80-year-old Iranian, is being called the world's dirtiest man. In an article published Jan. 6, he told the Tehran Times that he hasn't bathed in 60 years...

Read More At:
http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/01/15/amou-haji-iran-hasnt-bathed-60-years_n_4602936.html
